citances.sentence: In support of the order sought, reliance was placed upon the terms of Order 24 r 5(1) of the Federal Court Rules and the decision of Her Honour Justice Bell J in Eubanks (for the United States of America) v Cannar [2003] NSWSC 1267 (" Cannar "). Reliance was also placed upon the fact that the answers given during the course of the examination were not as yet evidence in the proceedings in which the examination has been ordered: cf. Eringa No 1 Native Title Claim v The State of South Australia [2007] FCA 182 at [7] per Mansfield J.
